properties.areaDesc: Santa Barbara County Central Coast; Santa Ynez Valley
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued February 8 at 12:42AM PST until February 8 at 9:00AM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Visibility one quarter mile or less in dense fog.

* WHERE...Santa Barbara County Central Coast and Santa Ynez
Valley.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM PST this morning.

* IMPACTS...Very low visibility will create dangerous driving
conditions.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...This includes Highways 1 and 101, and
State Routes 154 and 246.
properties.instruction:
If driving, slow down, use your headlights, and leave plenty of
distance ahead of you.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM PST THIS MORNING
